item.title: Gisela Valcárcel after fine Gabriela Herrera for S/ 56,000: “Contracts have obligations”
item.description: Gisela Valcárcel after fine Gabriela Herrera for S/ 56,000: “Contracts have obligations” Gabriela Herrera He surprised the public after revealing that he will have to face a penalty of 56,000 soles for having declared the program “Love and Fire” when he was participating in the reality show “El gran show”.
